    <item>
      <title>监管机构称英国政府机构易受网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/uk-government-agencies-vulnerable-to-cyberattacks-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[监管机构发现，英国政府部门运营着数百个过时的计算机系统，未能达到自身的网络安全目标，增加了遭受黑客攻击的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/uk-government-agencies-vulnerable-to-cyberattacks-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的资金冻结若继续实施，可能会触及《芯片法案》</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-s-funding-freeze-risks-hitting-chips-act-if-it-proceeds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，特朗普政府下令冻结联邦资金，目前该举措遭到联邦法官阻挠，如果允许其继续进行，可能会扰乱 520 亿美元的半导体补贴计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-s-funding-freeze-risks-hitting-chips-act-if-it-proceeds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Arm 中国任命新 CEO 以应对特朗普时代的芯片地缘政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/arm-china-picks-new-ceo-to-parry-chip-geopolitics-in-trump-era</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Arm Holdings Plc 的中国合资公司正在任命一位本地芯片资深人士担任其新任首席执行官，寻求​​巩固领导层，以更好地应对快速的地缘政治和技术变革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/arm-china-picks-new-ceo-to-parry-chip-geopolitics-in-trump-era</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
